title: AB Update; Preseason Week 1 Winners and Losers
itunes:title: AB Update; Preseason Week 1 Winners and Losers
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including the latest update with Antonio Brown and the Raiders (5:03) and an in depth kicker roundup you can't get anywhere else. (10:34) The heroes go through all of the winners and losers of preseason week 1. (25:19)
